h%E1%BB%A5/poem-3OQubNxaQmrMbk6IMp4qcA">Thù Chu giám kỷ Tứ Phụ - 酬朱監紀四輔</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/C%E1%BB%91-Vi%C3%AAm-V%C5%A9/author-py5Vb_484Rgr_jQ_nkfQjw">Cố Viêm Vũ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Th%C3%B4ng/Thu%E1%BA%ADt-c%E1%BA%A3m/poem-K5SGI9bzes4LFZD5eOaHWQ">Thuật cảm - 述感</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Th%C3%B4ng/author-rfaS1tOCWjWB9PkLJ5MHxw">Nguyễn Thông</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Ki%E1%BA%BFn/Thu%E1%BB%B7-phu-giao/poem-YNycjtFVEV-cAg2Oi9Zp8A">Thuỷ phu giao - 水夫謠</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Ki%E1%BA%BFn/author-Xw0ALUMVQ06c4vUGFngNbA">Vương Kiến</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Tu%C3%BD-th%C3%AC-ca-T%E1%BA%B7ng-Qu%E1%BA%A3ng-V%C4%83n-qu%C3%A1n-b%C3%A1c-s%C4%A9-Tr%E1%BB%8Bnh-Ki%E1%BB%81n/poem-3ntr8of8WpqEN_ETWKq8Eg">Tuý thì ca - Tặng Quảng Văn quán bác sĩ Trịnh Kiền - 醉時歌－贈廣文館博士鄭虔</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
